headline: Intuit’s AI-Driven Expert Platform Redefines Tax Filing with ‘Done-For-You’ Experiences
summary: MOUNTAIN VIEW, Calif., December 05, 2024--Intuit Inc. (Nasdaq: INTU), the global financial technology platform that makes Intuit TurboTax, Credit Karma, QuickBooks, and Mailchimp, today announced its tax platform offerings for personal and small business filers.
